   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>PREFACE</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>In order to facilitate fellowship between the churches and communication among the saints in various localities, Watchman Nee published Collection of Newsletters at the end of 1933.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>Its origin is explained in his open letter to all the brothers and sisters in the first issue of the magazine.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>Twelve issues were published over a period of two and a half years, with the last issue being published in July 1935.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>We have placed Issue Nos.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>1 through 9 in Volume 25 and Issue Nos.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>10 through 12 in Volume 26 of The Collected Works.</S>
   </TEXT>
